'''2015年8月博爾諾州炸彈襲擊'''，是指2015年8月[[尼日利亞|尼日利亞]][[博爾諾州|博爾諾州]]一所市場內發生的炸彈襲擊事件，共造成50人死亡、50人受傷。[[博科聖地|博科聖地]]被認為是這宗襲擊的主兇。

== 過程 ==
2015年8月11日下午，尼日利亚博爾諾州一所市场內有[[炸弹|炸弹]]爆炸；當時，這所市场剛剛進入繁忙時段，現場人流頗多<ref name=horror>{{cite news |title=Villagers describe horror of Borno market bombing |url=http://www.vanguardngr.com/2015/08/villagers-describe-horror-of-borno-market-bombing/ |accessdate=2015-09-13 |date=2015-08-12 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150913024523/http://www.vanguardngr.com/2015/08/villagers-describe-horror-of-borno-market-bombing/ |archivedate=2015-09-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。有人把炸弹藏在一個用作[[噴霧器|噴霧器]]的[[背包|背包]]內，再在市场放下該背包<ref name=deaths>{{cite news |author1=Jola Sotubo |title=Borno Bombing Update: 50 dead, 50 injured in market blast |url=http://pulse.ng/local/borno-bombing-update-50-dead-50-injured-in-market-blast-id4063700.html |accessdate=2015-09-13 |agency=Pulse.ng |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150913025403/http://pulse.ng/local/borno-bombing-update-50-dead-50-injured-in-market-blast-id4063700.html |archivedate=2015-09-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref>；炸弹被放在市场中央，它原先的位置在爆炸後被炸出一個大洞<ref>{{cite news |author1=Abdulkareem Haruna |title=Bomb Kills 20 In Borno Village Market Attack |url=http://leadership.ng/news/453343/bomb-kills-20-in-borno-village-market-attack |accessdate=2015-09-13 |agency=Leadership Newspaper |date=2015-08-12 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150913025255/http://leadership.ng/news/453343/bomb-kills-20-in-borno-village-market-attack |archivedate=2015-09-13 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。爆炸發生後，各類物品散滿一地，現場民眾驚慌地逃跑，有些傷者試圖逃離現場，但在途中死去；售賣[[流動電話|流動電話]]的分區顯得一片混亂，那裡的地面上有很多[[屍體|屍體]]，還滿佈[[血液|血液]]和肉塊<ref name=horror/>。

事發後，47名死者和最少50名傷者被送到博爾諾州的比烏總醫院<ref>{{cite news |title=Bomb blast rocks market in Nigeria's Borno State, 47 killed |url=http://www.iran-daily.com/News/124339.html |accessdate=2015-09-13 |agency=IRAN DAILY |date=2015-08-11 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150913041650/http://www.iran-daily.com/News/124339.html |archivedate=2015-09-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。有{{link-en|義務警員|Vigilante}}團體參與救援，協助把25名傷者送院救治<ref>{{cite news |title=Borno Market Bomb Attack Kills At Least 20 |url=http://thewillnigeria.com/news/borno-market-bomb-attack-kills-at-least-20/ |accessdate=2015-09-13 |agency=THEWILL |date=2015-08-11 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150913042329/http://thewillnigeria.com/news/borno-market-bomb-attack-kills-at-least-20/ |archivedate=2015-09-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。截至8月12日，是次炸彈襲擊共造成50人死亡、50人受傷<ref name=deaths/>。

== 責任和反應 ==
恐怖組織博科圣地企圖在尼日利亞东北部建立一個[[伊斯蘭國_(政權形式)|伊斯蘭國政權]]，該組織被指曾在事發地區一帶殺害數百人<ref name=boko>{{cite news |title=Suspected Boko Haram bomb in Nigerian market kills about 50 |url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/aug/12/suspected-boko-haram-bomb-in-nigerian-market-kills-about-50 |accessdate=2015-09-13 |agency=The Guardian |date=2015-08-12 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150813044926/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/aug/12/suspected-boko-haram-bomb-in-nigerian-market-kills-about-50 |archivedate=2015-08-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref>；博尔诺州位於尼日利亞东北部，亦是博科圣地恐怖份子的活躍地<ref>{{cite news |author1=刘晓朋 (编) |author2=杨旸 |author3=程光明 |title=尼日利亚东北部一市场遭炸弹袭击 48人死亡 |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2015-08/12/c_1116220375.htm |accessdate=2015-09-13 |agency=新华网 |date=2015-08-12 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150913053359/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2015-08/12/c_1116220375.htm |archivedate=2015-09-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。截至2015年8月12日，沒有任何個人或組織承認發動是次襲擊<ref name=boko/>；但是，尼日利亚有關当局認為博科圣地是這宗爆炸案的主兇<ref name=voa>{{cite news |title=美国谴责尼日利亚暴力袭击事件 |url=http://m.voachinese.com/a/Nigeria-violence-20150812/2914665.html |accessdate=2015-09-13 |agency=美国之音 |date=2015-08-12 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150913053448/http://m.voachinese.com/a/Nigeria-violence-20150812/2914665.html |archivedate=2015-09-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

[[美國|美國]]當局對是次炸彈襲擊表示强烈谴责<ref name=voa/>，[[尼日利亞總統|尼日利亞總統]][[穆罕默杜·布哈里|穆罕默杜·布哈里]]則承諾會粉碎博科聖地<ref>{{cite news |title=Nigeria market blast 'kills 28 in Borno' |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-33866129 |accessdate=2015-09-13 |agency=BBC |date=2015-08-12 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150913093122/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-33866129 |archivedate=2015-09-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

